New Records: Victor Wembanyama has 57 double-doubles in 101 career games
Key Match Events: Jokic scored nine points in overtime to seal the win
Vassell missed a contested layup, but tipped in the rebound, to tie the game at 108 with 14 seconds remaining in regulation
Jokic missed a 19-footer over Wembanyama with two seconds remaining to close regulation
Jokic scored his 44th point on a layup to put Denver up 115-108 with 2:27 remaining in OT
Post-Match Reflections: Nikola Jokic praised Victor Wembanyama, saying he will be'remembered forever' in the league
Miscellaneous Highlights: The teams split the home-and-home series on consecutive nights
Wembanyama was scoreless and without a rebound in OT
Denver's five-man bench accounted for 18 points and 21 rebounds
Julian Champagnie was 3-for-4 on 3-pointers in the two-game set against Denver
Wembanyama is averaging 30.6 points and 11.7 rebounds in his last nine games
Others: Zach Collins and Russell Westbrook each received a technical foul in the first quarter after taunting one another
